 잘먹더라구요. ^^               탱글탱글 제철인 굴을 넣어 끓인 굴국!   한입 하실래요??     칼칼한 굴국을 원하신다면 여기에 매운고추 조금만 넣어도 맛있어요~   신랑은 칼칼한걸 좋아해서   이 상태에서 매운고추를 몇조각 넣어줬더니   저나 신랑이 먹기에는 딱! 좋더라구욤~ ^^                 5살 도도녀도 너무너무 잘 먹고!   3살 순딩양도 너무너무 잘 먹는 굴국!   아이들 끓여줄거면 요렇게 한번 끓여줘보세요~ ^^     아이들마다 다르겠지만 울 애들은 놀라울정도로 잘 먹어서리.. ^^                 저두 오늘아침 아이들과 함께 굴국으로 든든한 한끼 해결했네요 ^^        ","images":["http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_296/eunokpw99_1416379094467Tbb34_JPEG/IMG_8496.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_85/eunokpw99_1416379094998uQO6Q_JPEG/IMG_8478.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141119_294/eunokpw99_1416379095434bSn1e_JPEG/IMG_8480.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141119_107/eunokpw99_1416379095906ufCVr_JPEG/IMG_8481.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141119_63/eunokpw99_1416379096246T1Aoi_JPEG/IMG_8482.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_204/eunokpw99_1416379096514Xf4lX_JPEG/IMG_8484.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_144/eunokpw99_14163790974524gMS8_JPEG/IMG_8485.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_41/eunokpw99_1416379097783ppErG_JPEG/IMG_8486.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141119_2/eunokpw99_1416379098034yzqbj_JPEG/IMG_8487.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141119_270/eunokpw99_1416379098395GdEkX_JPEG/IMG_8488.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_112/eunokpw99_1416379098705NCTLY_JPEG/IMG_8489.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_85/eunokpw99_1416379098985n2XJ9_JPEG/IMG_8490.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141119_44/eunokpw99_1416379099293bG0lJ_JPEG/IMG_8491.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_233/eunokpw99_1416379099615G1sre_JPEG/IMG_8492.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141119_235/eunokpw99_1416379100161WfdRe_JPEG/IMG_8493.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141119_41/eunokpw99_1416379100457033ND_JPEG/IMG_8494.